3b:["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["Once all schema designs are completed, the ",["$","$L1b",null,{"href":"/api/interfaces/_autobe_interface.AutoBePrismaValidateEvent.html","prefetch":"$undefined","className":"x:focus-visible:nextra-focus x:text-primary-600 x:underline x:hover:no-underline x:decoration-from-font x:[text-underline-position:from-font]","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"AutoBePrismaValidateEvent"}]}]," event is triggered, and ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"@autobe"}],"’s built-in Prisma compiler validates the table designs. 6b9:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     *"}]}]
6ba:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * The `name` must be unique within the API's accessor namespace. The"}]}]
6bb:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * accessor is formed by combining the path segments (excluding parameters)"}]}]

6bf:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     *"}]}]
6c0:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * 1. Extract non-parameter segments from the path (remove `{...}` parts)"}]}]
6c1:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * 2. Join segments with dots"}]}]
6c2:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * 3. Append the operation name"}]}]

6ca:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * - Path: `/auth/login`, Name: `signIn` → Accessor: `auth.login.signIn`"}]}]

6d0:["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#E36209","--shiki-dark":"#FFAB70"},"children":"    name"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#D73A49","--shiki-dark":"#F97583"},"children":":"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#005CC5","--shiki-dark":"#79B8FF"},"children":" string"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#D73A49","--shiki-dark":"#F97583"},"children":" &"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6F42C1","--shiki-dark":"#B392F0"},"children":" CamelCasePattern"}],["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#24292E","--shiki-dark":"#E1E4E8"},"children":";"}]]}]
6d1:["$","span",null,{"children":" "}]

6d3:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * Prerequisites for this API operation."}]}]

6d5:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * The `prerequisites` field defines API operations that must be"}]}]
6d6:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * successfully executed before this operation can be performed. This"}]}]
6d7:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * creates an explicit dependency chain between API endpoints, ensuring"}]}]
6d8:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * proper execution order and data availability."}]}]

6da:["$","span",null,{"children":["$","span",null,{"style":{"--shiki-light":"#6A737D","--shiki-dark":"#6A737D"},"children":"     * ## CRITICAL WARNING: Authentication Prerequisites"}]}]
